1 - Repo
    ----

    Proofcase collects small, self-sufficient Rocq proofs, mostly as
    accompanying formulations to papers and notes.


2 - Style
    -----

    Formalizations are written with an emphasis on clarity, adhering
    to standard Rocq best practices and modern conventions.


3 - Files
    -----

    ./theories/                 The primary .v file directory.

    ./builders/                 Automation tools.

    ./builders/_CoqProject      Logical paths for compilation.


